<div class="ayahs rtl" dir="rtl">
<p class="ayah 75-1" id="1" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Nay!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُقْسِمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">I swear</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِيَوْمِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">by (the) Day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْقِيَـٰمَةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the Resurrection.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>1<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
