<p class="ayah 75-4" id="4" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Nay!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَـٰدِرِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[We are] able</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">on</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نُّسَوِّىَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We can restore</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَنَانَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">his fingertips.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>4<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 75-5" id="5" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Nay!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُرِيدُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Desires</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[the] man</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِيَفْجُرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to give (the) lie</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمَامَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to) what is before him.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>5<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 75-6" id="6" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَسْــَٔلُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He asks,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَيَّانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`When</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَوْمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is the) Day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْقِيَـٰمَةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the Resurrection?`</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>6<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 75-7" id="7" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَإِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَرِقَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">is dazzled</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْبَصَرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the vision,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>7<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 75-8" id="8" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَخَسَفَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And becomes dark</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْقَمَرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the moon,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>8<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 75-9" id="9" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَجُمِعَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And are joined</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلشَّمْسُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the sun</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْقَمَرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the moon,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>9<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
