<p class="ayah 75-11" id="11" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">By no means!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(There is) no</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَزَرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">refuge.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>11<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 75-12" id="12" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">To</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your Lord,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَوْمَئِذٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that Day,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمُسْتَقَرُّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) the place of rest.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>12<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 75-13" id="13" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُنَبَّؤُاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Will be informed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[the] man</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَوْمَئِذِۭ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that Day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَدَّمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he sent forth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَخَّرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and kept back.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>13<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 75-14" id="14" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَلِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Nay!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[The] man</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">against</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَفْسِهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">himself</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَصِيرَةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will be) a witness.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>14<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 75-15" id="15" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Even if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَلْقَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he presents</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَعَاذِيرَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">his excuses.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>15<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 75-16" id="16" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُحَرِّكْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">move</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِسَانَكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your tongue</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِتَعْجَلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to hasten</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِهِۦٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with it.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>16<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 75-17" id="17" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">upon Us</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَمْعَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) its collection</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقُرْءَانَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and its recitation.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>17<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 75-18" id="18" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَإِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَرَأْنَـٰهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We have recited it,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱتَّبِعْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then follow</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُرْءَانَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">its recitation.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>18<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 75-19" id="19" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ثُمَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">upon Us</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَيَانَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) its explanation.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>19<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 75-20" id="20" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">No!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">But</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُحِبُّونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you love</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْعَاجِلَةَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the immediate,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>20<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 75-21" id="21" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَتَذَرُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And leave</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَخِرَةَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Hereafter.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>21<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 75-22" id="22" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وُجُوهٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Faces</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَوْمَئِذٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that Day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَّاضِرَةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will be) radiant,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>22<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 75-23" id="23" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Towards</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَاظِرَةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">looking,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>23<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 75-24" id="24" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَوُجُوهٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And faces</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَوْمَئِذِۭ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that Day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَاسِرَةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will be) distorted,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>24<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 75-25" id="25" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَظُنُّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Thinking</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُفْعَلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will be done</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَاقِرَةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">backbreaking.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>25<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 75-26" id="26" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَلَّآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">No!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">When</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَلَغَتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it reaches</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلتَّرَاقِىَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the collar bones</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>26<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 75-27" id="27" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقِيلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And it is said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَنْۜ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَاقٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will) cure?`</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>27<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
